021/**
022 * PatternData
023 *
024 * @author creatorfromhell
025 * @since 0.2.0.0
026 */
027public class PatternData {
028
029  protected String color;
030  protected String pattern;
031
032  public PatternData(final String color, final String pattern) {
033
034    this.color = color;
035    this.pattern = pattern;
036  }
037
038  public String getColor() {
039
040    return color;
041  }
042
043  public void setColor(final String color) {
044
045    this.color = color;
046  }
047
048  public String getPattern() {
049
050    return pattern;
051  }
052
053  public void setPattern(final String pattern) {
054
055    this.pattern = pattern;
056  }
057}
